targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  count(1) as existing
FROM
  abstracto.channel
WHERE 
deleted = false

SELECT
  count(1) as deleted
FROM
  abstracto.channel
WHERE 
deleted = true

SELECT
  count(1) as existing
FROM
  abstracto.role
where
deleted = false

SELECT
  count(1) as deleted
FROM
  abstracto.role
where
deleted = true

SELECT
  count(1) as group
FROM
  abstracto.profanity_group

SELECT
  count(1) as regex
FROM
  abstracto.profanity_regex

SELECT
  count(1) AS "Buttons"
  
FROM abstracto.component_payload
WHERE type = 'BUTTON'

SELECT
  count(1) AS "Selections"
  
FROM abstracto.component_payload
WHERE type = 'SELECTION'

SELECT
  count(1) as "Decayed"
FROM
  abstracto.warning
WHERE decayed = true

SELECT
  count(1) as "Active"
FROM
  abstracto.warning
WHERE decayed = false

SELECT
  count(1) as "Active"
FROM
  abstracto.mute
WHERE mute_ended = false

SELECT
  count(1) as "Ended"
FROM
  abstracto.mute
WHERE mute_ended = true

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.profanity_use
WHERE 
  verified = true

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.profanity_use
WHERE 
  confirmed = true

with starred_users as (
SELECT
  count(1) as count
FROM
  abstracto.starboard_post
  GROUP BY author_user_in_server_id
)
SELECT count(1) from starred_users

with starring_users as (
SELECT
  count(1) as count
FROM
  abstracto.starboard_post_reaction
  GROUP BY reactor_user_in_server_id
)
SELECT count(1) from starring_users

SELECT 
  role_id as "Role ID",
  count(1) as "Member count"
FROM 
  abstracto.user_experience
  GROUP BY role_id

  count(1)

 abstracto.user_experience

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.tracked_emote
WHERE 
  tracking_enabled = true

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.tracked_emote
WHERE 
  tracking_enabled = false

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.tracked_emote
WHERE 
  deleted = true

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.tracked_emote
WHERE 
  animated = true

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.tracked_emote
WHERE 
  external = true

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.used_emote
WHERE 
  use_date = CURRENT_DATE

SELECT
  count(1)
FROM
  abstracto.used_emote
WHERE 
  use_date > CURRENT_DATE - 7

  count(1)
